official_title: To award a congressional gold medal to Edward William Brooke III in recognition of his unprecedented and enduring service to our Nation.
short_title: Edward William Brooke III Congressional Gold Medal Act

summary.text: Edward William Brooke III Congressional Gold Medal Act - Awards a congressional gold medal to Edward William Brooke III, the first African American elected by popular vote to the U.S. Senate, in recognition of his unprecedented and enduring service to our Nation.
